Kubernetes: 容器编排
- Automation of
    - Deployment
    - Management
    - Scaling
    - Networking
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
What is k8s?
- open source orchestration container tool
ps: container could be docker containers or from some other technology
- helps you managed containerized applications in diff envi

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Node

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Pod:
- Smallest unit of K8s
- Abstraction over container
- Usually 1 application per Pod, or with some help container, side service
- Each Pod gets its own IP address
- New IP address on re-creation

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Service:
- permanent IP address
- lifecycle of Pod and Service NOT connected

